	* rfc2047.c: Removing a superfluous (unsigned char) cast in an IsPrint
	argument.

Mon Jul 13 10:50:39 1998  Thomas Roessler  <roessler@guug.de>

	* doc/mutt.sgml, doc/mutt.man, doc/Makefile.in:
